%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"b8f5dcd9a98b4d8d6c16f16e1d1fe31174f1a6ae","tid":2068309,"uid":47356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:02:55.000Z","msg":"三萬個死得哂的話, 羅范椒芬冚家都要陪警察"},{"pid":"82c27a4513dabaefd5c83a879c57bffa99694e1b","tid":2068309,"uid":332804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:04:22.000Z","msg":"希望十年後嘅香港係一個獨立唔受中共影響嘅香港。"},{"pid":"1c3c5da9f735bc80e249985ccc0574108ea8fde3","tid":2068309,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2d33136b576f40063ffc6cdeca607b6d77444c03","tid":2068309,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:00:55.000Z","msg":"期望十年後香港是一個唔再奶共既社會<br />\n大陸落任何命令香港所有人都唔SHOW 佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:04:31.000Z","msg":"認輸師突然正常返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c10113eebe787ccaafb8cd84e6a3bf5deb3448","tid":2068309,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:04:31.000Z","msg":"10年我哋已經移曬民，成班藍絲俾都唔想住"},{"pid":"dba09221a44be4c3216d9766a02029dd3cb9852c","tid":2068309,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59a51fde37b19e0a3b26521fba8ea56df6e68f93"